<head>
@{
            <environment include="Development">
                <link href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" />
            </environment>
            <environment exclude="Development">
                <link href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" asp-append-version="true" />
            </environment>

        ViewBag.Mobile = 0;
 }
    @{
        ViewBag.Canonical = @String.Format("https://www.tripmasters.com/about_us");

    }
<style>
.chatUs{height: 22px!important;font-size: 12px!important;}
 .table{width:980px!important;margin:0 auto}
 .secTopHeader{height:140px!important} 
 .adotDecor{color:white!important}
.dvhChat{width:30%!important}
.dvpagecontainer {max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto}
.about {color: #2A2C5D;font-size: 60px;margin-top: 60px;margin-bottom: 20px}
.our {margin-top: 82px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: #7387C3;border-left-width: 5px;padding-left: 29px}
.our h2.p1 {color: #7387C3;font-size: 50px;margin-bottom: 0px;}
.our h2.p2 {color: #7387C3;font-size: 50px;font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0px;font-family: Verdana;}
.text {color: #666666;font-size: 18px;font-family: Verdana, Regular;line-height: 1.8}
.text p{color: #666666;font-size: 18px;font-family: Verdana, Regular;line-height: 1.8}
.text p:nth-child(2) { padding-top: 25px;}
.better {width: 100%;border-top-color: #666666;border-bottom-color: #666666;border-bottom-style: solid;border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-top-width: 1px;color: #7387C3;font-size: 40px;text-align: center;padding: 27px 0;margin: 100px auto}
#list {font-size: 18px; color: #666666;list-style: none;padding-left: 0px;}
 #list li{padding: 10px 0;}
.unicode {color: #FBA919;width: 8px;height: 8px;padding-right: 10px;}
.image {text-align: center;margin-bottom: 25px;}
.BBB {color: #24285F;font-size: 30px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 17px}
.BBB span {color: #f9a719;}
.airline {color: #999999;font-size: 23px;margin-bottom: 60px;}
.con {color: #707070;font-size: 24px;text-align: center;}
.travels {color: #24285F;font-size: 50px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 89px;}
 @@media only screen and (max-width:780px) {
    /* For mobile phones: */
    .dvpagecontainer{background-color:#F2F2F2;width:100%}
    div.mobile{background-color:white;border:1px solid #CCCCCC;}
    .about{font-size:35px;margin-top:25px;margin-left:11px}
    .our{margin-top:54px;margin-bottom:80px;padding-left:15px;margin-left:11px;border-left-width:3px;}
    .our .p1{font-size:28px!important;}
    .our .p2{font-size:29px!important;}
     .text{font-size:14px;line-height: 1.8;padding-right:17px}
     .text p{font-size:14px;line-height: 1.8;padding-right:17px}
    .better{font-size:15px;width: 90%;font-weight:bold}
    #list{font-size:14px;}
  .unicode{display:none;}
  .better{margin:50px auto}
  .image{margin-bottom:17px;height:45px;}
  .BBB{font-size:19px;margin-bottom:20px;}
  .airline{font-size:15px;text-align:center;}
  .con{font-size:14px}
  .travels{font-size:29px;margin-bottom:65px;}
    }
</style>
</head>

<section class="dvpagecontainer">
    <div class="mobile">
        <h1 class="about">About Us</h1>
        <div class="our">
            <h2 class="p1">OUR</h2>
            <h2 class="p2">HISTORY</h2>
            <div class="text">
                <p>
                    Tripmasters is a second-generation family travel business based in Silver Spring MD. We started as a customizer of vacations to Peru back in 1984.
                    We have gradually and carefully expanded our destinations to include most of Latin America, Europe, Asia and the Pacific. We maintain our focus on dynamically customizing multi-destination vacation itineraries. Our agents, trip building and customization tools make it easy to plan flexible complex trips. Our long term productive relationships with airlines, hotels and partners at each destination allow us to provide our services reliably and at a compelling value to you.
           
            </p>
            <p>
                We have built suggested itineraries which you can price and customize according to your budget and how much time you want to spend in each destination. We curate and recommend hotels, transportation and activities in each stop of your itinerary. You can build and price all this in seconds.
                If you can't find the exact itinerary you want from our suggested itineraries you can use our booking tools to build your own itinerary in seconds. Our agents are also available 7 days a week from 8AM to Midnight ET to help craft your vacation.
            </p>
        </div>
        </div>


      <div class="our">
            <h2 class="p1">OUR</h2>
            <h2 class="p2">MISSION</h2>
                <p class="text">
                    Our mission is to delight our customers such that they become repeat customers and enthusiastically recommend us to friends and family.
                    The better we accomplish this mission, the more resources we have to improve the lives of our workers and those in need.
                </p>
      </div>

        <div class="our">
            <h2 class="p1">OUR</h2>
            <h2 class="p2">VALUES</h2>
            <ul id="list">
                <li style="font-size:18px"><span class="unicode">&#x25A0;</span>We believe that improving our product and service is an endless process. </li>
                <li style="font-size:18px"><span class="unicode">&#x25A0;</span>We are honest to our customers, employees and suppliers.</li>
                <li style="font-size:18px"><span class="unicode">&#x25A0;</span>We believe business has a higher purpose than the bottom line. </li>
                <li style="font-size:18px"><span class="unicode">&#x25A0;</span>We invest the fruits of our success to continuously enhance the lives of our workers.The more we succeed the more their lives improve.</li>
                <li style="font-size:18px"><span class="unicode">&#x25A0;</span>We give back to the world by giving an ever increasing portion of our earnings to Unicef and Children Incorporated, both focusing on improving children's lives in disadvantaged circumstances.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="better">
            The better we do the more good we do.
        </div>
        <div class="image"><img class="image" src="https://pictures.tripmasters.com/siteassets/d/TM_logo%20400%20x%2097px-01.png" /></div>
        <p class="BBB">is an <span><b>A+</b></span> rated business by the BBB.</p>
        <p class="airline">A fully bonded travel business certified by IATA and the ARC (Airline Reporting Corporation).</p>
        <p class="con">For your convenience we accept</p>
        <div class="image"><img src="https://pictures.tripmasters.com/siteassets/d/creditcards.png" /></div>
        <p class="travels">Happy Travels!</p>
    </div>
</section>